info.author: Jurgen Thies
info.description:
The LayoutEditor is a program to design and edit layout for IC/MEMS fabrication.
The python modul enables not only scripting in the very popular scripting
language python, but also allows anyone to adjust, extend and embed the
LayoutEditor in a very flexible way. The LayoutEditor main window and a new
'juspertor library manager' is written in python itself and can be modified to
your demands
info.license: different licenses, basic version under GPL
info.name: LayoutEditor
